#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn40.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn40.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 40 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 40 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Moggallānavagga "
msgstr "1. By Moggallāna "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn40.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Animittapañhāsutta "
msgstr "9. A Question About the Signless "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.269, sc1
msgctxt "sn40.9:1.1"
msgid "“‘Animitto cetosamādhi, animitto cetosamādhī’ti vuccati. "
msgstr "“They speak of this thing called the ‘signless immersion of the heart’. "

msgctxt "sn40.9:1.2"
msgid "Katamo nu kho animitto cetosamādhīti? "
msgstr "What is the signless immersion of the heart? "

msgctxt "sn40.9:1.3"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, etadahosi: "
msgstr "It occurred to me: "

msgctxt "sn40.9:1.4"
msgid "‘idha bhikkhu sabbanimittānaṃ amanasikārā animittaṃ cetosamādhiṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "‘It’s when a mendicant, not focusing on any signs, enters and remains in the signless immersion of the heart. "

msgctxt "sn40.9:1.5"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati animitto cetosamādhī’ti. "
msgstr "This is called the signless immersion of the heart.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.9:1.6"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, sabbanimittānaṃ amanasikārā animittaṃ cetosamādhiṃ upasampajja viharāmi. "
msgstr "And so … I was entering and remaining in the signless immersion of the heart. "

msgctxt "sn40.9:1.7"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ, āvuso, iminā vihārena viharato nimittānusāri viññāṇaṃ hoti. "
msgstr "While I was in that meditation, my consciousness followed after signs. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn40.9:2.1"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ, āvuso, bhagavā iddhiyā upasaṅkamitvā etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the Buddha came up to me with his psychic power and said, "

msgctxt "sn40.9:2.2"
msgid "‘moggallāna, moggallāna. "
msgstr "‘Moggallāna, Moggallāna! "

msgctxt "sn40.9:2.3"
msgid "Mā, brāhmaṇa, animittaṃ cetosamādhiṃ pamādo, animitte cetosamādhismiṃ cittaṃ saṇṭhapehi, animitte cetosamādhismiṃ cittaṃ ekodiṃ karohi, animitte cetosamādhismiṃ cittaṃ samādahā’ti. "
msgstr "Don’t neglect the signless immersion of the heart, brahmin! Settle your mind in the signless immersion of the heart; unify your mind and immerse it in the signless immersion of the heart.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.9:2.4"
msgid "So khvāhaṃ, āvuso, aparena samayena sabbanimittānaṃ amanasikārā animittaṃ cetosamādhiṃ upasampajja vihāsiṃ. "
msgstr "And so, after some time … I entered and remained in the signless immersion of the heart. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn40.9:2.5"
msgid "Yañhi taṃ, āvuso, sammā vadamāno vadeyya: "
msgstr "So if anyone should be rightly called "

msgctxt "sn40.9:2.6"
msgid "‘satthārānuggahito sāvako mahābhiññataṃ patto’ti, mamaṃ taṃ sammā vadamāno vadeyya: "
msgstr "a disciple who attained to great direct knowledge with help from the Teacher, it’s me.” "

msgctxt "sn40.9:2.7"
msgid "‘satthārānuggahito sāvako mahābhiññataṃ patto’”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn40.9:2.8"
msgid "Navamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

